        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         1-2: Stuff I'm likely to swap in and out.  Heals, pet and pet buff, Gate, Lich.</P><P>3-4: Common buffs, or things that if I did switch out I'd want back fast.  Shield, Skin, Harmshield, DMF, etc., Grim Aura and Vampiric Embrace just for my own amusement.</P><P>5-6: Less common buffs and things.  Resist Cold/Disease, Shadow Sight, IVU, etc.</P><P>7-8: Undead spells. Undead charm, Banish, Shackle, Hungry Earth, Torment, etc.</P><P>9-10: Current best DOT selection, lifetaps, Screaming Terror, Fear.</P><P>11-12: DDs and Debuffs and less effective DOTs.</P><P>13-14: Weird utility stuff.  Bind Affinity, Identify, Locate/Track/Summon Corpse, Ward Undead for practicing evocation, etc.</P><P>15: True North.  It's so special it has its own page.</P><P>20+: Spells I never use any more.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=247832" target="_blank">Morty Undercrypt</a>, Keeper of the <a href="http://www.necrognomicon.com/" target="_blank">NecroGnomicon</a><BR><font size=1>"I am the truth, and the truth shall make you flee."</font id=size1><BR>E'ci<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
