        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Pages 3 and 4 are spells that I constantly swap out</P><P>pages 1 and 2 are dots and lifetaps and root and ST</P><P>pages 5 and 6 are pets other grp type spells</P><P>When I open my spell book I made a macro with /book 3 that way I always open up to my hot swap spells and Im only 1 page left or 1 page right to other spells I need...</P><P>Rest spell after page 6 are utility type spells. Old ass spells get put back to book 40 and beyond..</P><P><font size=1>Bloogledadingle Quaqqlebunk | <b>Warlock</b>| Povar </font id=size1><BR><font size=1>Dark Legion</font id=size1><BR><img src=icon_smile_evil.gif border=0 align=middle><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
